metadata.name: Eddie's Bagel & Coffee
metadata.description:
Eddie's Bagel & Coffee - 3.67/5  
  
Store  
A small store arranged in an unusual but compelling manor - not hexagonal but in the realm of unusual polygons. A fast staff, courteous and efficient. Limited add-ons across the board - pastries, drinks and other snacks.  
3.5/5  
  
Bagel  
Medium-large bagel. Toppings both sides, salt crystals included. Existing in the twilight between fresh and old; certainly not served hot. A tough bagel, but a surprisingly pleasant crunchiness from the shell that synergizes well with the topping density. A bagel greater than the sum of its parts.  
3.75/5  
  
Cream Cheese  
Served case cold. Bagel store fresh. A slight tang with no overcheese. A medium-sized scallion chop. Compliments the bagel without overriding it.  
3.75/5
